abstract: American Hannah Kearney wins dual moguls world title in Kreischberg, Austria; Canadian Mikael Kingsbury earns men's gold medal.
lead_paragraph: The American Hannah Kearney won the world title in dual moguls in Kreischberg, Austria, and Mikael Kingsbury of Canada earned the men’s gold medal.
snippet: The American Hannah Kearney won the world title in dual moguls in Kreischberg, Austria, and Mikael Kingsbury of Canada earned the men’s gold medal.

headline.main: American Captures Her First Title in Dual Moguls
